Padhānassāti ‘raññopuriso-bhirūpo’tettha abhirūpasāpekkhassa purisassa visesanattenevāvisesanaṃ tenevā 
Note { id=15, line='105', referenceLine='89', original='visesanaṃ tenevā (potthake)', type='auto', previous='Padhānassāti ‘raññopuriso-bhirūpo’tettha abhirūpasāpekkhassa purisassa visesanattenevā '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='visesanattenevā'}
	Alternative{lang='potthake', text='visesanaṃ tenevā'}}
ppadhānaṃ, samāsāvayavabhūtaṃ rājānaṃ pati visessabhāvenāviphalitasakatthatāya padhānabhūtassa purisassa. Ādisaddena ‘rājapurisassa dassanīyassa geha’nti saṅgaṇhāti.

Yattha brāhmaṇā aññova bhavatītyevaṃ vākyenātthantaravidhānā vidhino padhānattaṃ, atthantaravidhānasāmatthiyeneva brāhmaṇassa paṭisedho patīyate, brāhmaṇassabrāhmaṇassā 
Note { id=18, line='120', referenceLine='109', original='brāhmaṇassā (potthake)', type='auto', previous='Yattha brāhmaṇā aññova bhavatītyevaṃ vākyenātthantaravidhānā vidhino padhānattaṃ, atthantaravidhānasāmatthiyeneva brāhmaṇassa paṭisedho patīyate, brāhmaṇassa '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='brāhmaṇassa'}
	Alternative{lang='potthake', text='brāhmaṇassā'}}
nivattane tadapekkhāyāññassa vidhānayogato sakapadena nañkhyena vidhibhāgī na vuccate, kiñcarahi aññasaddena… pariyudāsanissayinoññasaddasseva vākye payogato’ añño brāhmaṇā abrāhmaṇo’ti, nañssaca syādyantena sāmatthiyaṃ, na tyādyantenetyekavākyatā… añño brāhmaṇā abrāhmaṇoti tattha tattha pariyudāsavuttittā.

Bahuttāti kiñcāpi vākye nesaṃvākyenevesaṃ 
Note { id=19, line='129', referenceLine='150', original='vākyenevesaṃ (potthake)', type='auto', previous='Bahuttāti kiñcāpi vākye nesaṃ '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='nesaṃ'}
	Alternative{lang='potthake', text='vākyenevesaṃ'}}
visuṃ bahvatthatā, na hi sāriputtamānayāti vutte moggallānassāpi sampaccayo bhavati, tathāpi yato vuttivisaye sahabhūtānamevesaṃ visuṃ bahvatthatā, tato tattha vacanīyassa atthassa saṅkhyātedena bahuttaṃ. Samāharaṇaṃ piṇḍīkaraṇavasena saṃharaṇaṃ samāhāro, so cevaṃ veditabboti dassetumāha ‘aññamaññe’ccādi.

Nanuceccādinā vuttaṃ codanaṃ nisedheti ‘tanne’ti. Tattha kāraṇamāha- ‘ghasaññattā’tyādi. Aghonanti ghaokāravajjitānaṃ, nanu itthi yamākāro gho, tathāsati napuṃsake so (na siyāti) parikappeti ‘napuṃsakattā ghattameva natthīti cedi’ti. Tampi neti yathā vuttampaṭikkhipitvā attheva napuṃsake ghattantinapuṃsakattanti 
Note { id=20, line='138', referenceLine='175', original='napuṃsakattanti (potthake)', type='auto', previous='Nanuceccādinā vuttaṃ codanaṃ nisedheti ‘tanne’ti. Tattha kāraṇamāha- ‘ghasaññattā’tyādi. Aghonanti ghaokāravajjitānaṃ, nanu itthi yamākāro gho, tathāsati napuṃsake so (na siyāti) parikappeti ‘napuṃsakattā ghattameva natthīti cedi’ti. Tampi neti yathā vuttampaṭikkhipitvā attheva napuṃsake ghattanti '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='ghattanti'}
	Alternative{lang='potthake', text='napuṃsakattanti'}}
 dassetumāha-chaṭṭhīsamāsasse’ccādi. Napuṃsake ghattassanapuṃsakattassa 
Note { id=21, line='147', referenceLine='175', original='napuṃsakattassa (potthake)', type='auto', previous=' dassetumāha-chaṭṭhīsamāsasse’ccādi. Napuṃsake ghattassa '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='ghattassa'}
	Alternative{lang='potthake', text='napuṃsakattassa'}}
sabbhāvameva samattheti napuṃsakattaṃ hi’ccādinā, pāribhāsikanti ettha suttamevādhippetaṃ, paribhāsāya nibbattaṃ pāribhāsikaṃ suttikanti attho. Ārabhitabbamevidaṃ suttaṃ (napuṃsakassāpi) rassattavidhānāyāti adhippāyo. Ghanissitampi kāriyanti ‘‘ghabrahmādīte’’tyādinā (2-60) vidhiyamānamekārādikāriyampi. Etaṃ ghanissitaṃ kāriyaṃ naca yuttanti sambandho. Ayuttattepi doso-yamāpatatevākyāsaṅkiyāha-‘nāyampidoso’ccādi, na rassassa ettheva laddhāvasarattā paṭhamaṃ tena paviṭṭhe… (ghani)ssitaṃ kāriyanti nāyampi doso paribhāsāva senāti mantabbaṃ. Salabhacchāye iti padacchedo.

nugāmī pana (potthake)vuttaṃ, tathā hi te evaṃ liṅgalakkhaṇa māhu (pā, 4-1-3 kāsikāyaṃ) ‘‘sāmaññavisesā itthattādayo gottādayo viya bahuppakārabyattiyoti 
Note { id=24, line='172', referenceLine='188', original='sāmaññāni ca tulyajātiyapadatthasādhāraṇattā tāni visesā ca añña maññehi vijātiyeti ca visissante byāvattanteti sāmaññavisesā. byañjīyantiā etehīti byattiyo sāmaññavisesānaṃ nissayā, bahuppakārā byatti yo yesaṃ sāmaññavisesānaṃ te tathāvuttāti– (kāsikāvivaraṇa pañjikā.)', type='auto', previous=' vuttaṃ, tathā hi te evaṃ liṅgalakkhaṇa māhu (pā, 4-1-3 kāsikāyaṃ) sāmaññavisesā itthattādayo gottādayo viya bahuppakārabyattiyoti '
